@host = http://localhost:8080
@token = 请先填入 mock-login 返回的 token
@deviceCode = 请填入设备编码

### 1. 查看设备目录
GET {{host}}/api/v1/devices/catalog
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 绑定多指标健康站
POST {{host}}/api/v1/devices
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceType": "HEALTH_COMBO_STATION",
  "vendorName": "Tongfeng",
  "deviceModel": "STATION-1",
  "serialNumber": "STATION-SN-001",
  "aliasName": "family-health-station"
}

### 3. 查看设备列表
GET {{host}}/api/v1/devices
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 查看设备总览
GET {{host}}/api/v1/devices/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 同步组合设备数据
POST {{host}}/api/v1/devices/{{deviceCode}}/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "metricType": "URIC_ACID",
      "externalEventId": "evt-ua-1",
      "measuredAt": "2026-04-29T08:00:00Z",
      "value": 502,
      "unit": "umol/L",
      "note": "device sync"
    },
    {
      "metricType": "HYDRATION",
      "externalEventId": "evt-hyd-1",
      "measuredAt": "2026-04-29T09:00:00Z",
      "waterIntakeMl": 900,
      "urineColorLevel": 4,
      "note": "smart cup sync"
    },
    {
      "metricType": "WEIGHT",
      "externalEventId": "evt-weight-1",
      "measuredAt": "2026-04-29T10:00:00Z",
      "value": 71.8,
      "unit": "kg",
      "note": "smart scale sync"
    },
    {
      "metricType": "BLOOD_PRESSURE",
      "externalEventId": "evt-bp-1",
      "measuredAt": "2026-04-29T10:05:00Z",
      "systolicPressure": 162,
      "diastolicPressure": 101,
      "pulseRate": 88,
      "unit": "mmHg",
      "note": "bp monitor sync"
    }
  ]
}

### 6. 查看同步历史
GET {{host}}/api/v1/devices/{{deviceCode}}/sync-events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. 查看同步后的设备总览
GET {{host}}/api/v1/devices/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. 绑定尿酸仪用于白名单校验
POST {{host}}/api/v1/devices
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceType": "URIC_ACID_METER",
  "vendorName": "Tongfeng",
  "deviceModel": "UA-1",
  "serialNumber": "UA-SN-GUARD-001",
  "aliasName": "ua-meter"
}

### 9. 非法同步示例：向尿酸仪写入血压
POST {{host}}/api/v1/devices/{{deviceCode}}/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "metricType": "BLOOD_PRESSURE",
      "externalEventId": "evt-bp-blocked-1",
      "measuredAt": "2026-04-29T10:05:00Z",
      "systolicPressure": 142,
      "diastolicPressure": 91,
      "pulseRate": 80,
      "unit": "mmHg",
      "note": "should be blocked"
    }
  ]
}
